# Keep the root build context lean — these are volume-mounted or irrelevant.
# NOTE: web/ SOURCE is deliberately INCLUDED (Dockerfile.single builds the SPA from it).
# Only its heavy/host-specific artifacts are dropped. Excluding web/ entirely here broke
# the single-container build whenever BuildKit (and its per-Dockerfile ignore file) was
# off — the classic builder only honors THIS file.
.git
.gitignore
data/
models/
reports/
presentations/
__pycache__/
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
.env
.env.*
*.xlsx
*.pptx
*.pdf
*.docx
*.~lock*
node_modules/
**/node_modules/
.svelte-kit/
**/.svelte-kit/
build/
web/build/
